《'''庭审专家'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Bull'''''}}）是一部[[美国|美国]]律政题材的[[电视剧|电视剧]]，以前《[[海军犯罪调查局|海军犯罪调查局]]》主演[[迈克·韦瑟利|迈克·韦瑟利]]为主要角色。[[CBS电视网|CBS电视网]]在2016年5月13日宣布订购该电视剧，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/training-day-bull-macgyver-the-great-indoors-matt-leblanc-jason-katims-cbs-series-1201755376/|title=Training Day, Bull, MacGyver,  Matt LeBlanc Comedy Picked Up By CBS|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2016-07-19|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327123108/https://deadline.com/2016/05/training-day-bull-macgyver-the-great-indoors-matt-leblanc-jason-katims-cbs-series-1201755376/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 并于同年7月20日开播本剧。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/cbs-fall-premiere-dates-2016-1201776569/|title=CBS Sets Fall 2016 Premiere Dates, Slates JonBenet Ramsey Limited Series|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2016-06-21|accessdate=2016-06-21|archive-date=2018-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180223214506/http://deadline.com/2016/06/cbs-fall-premiere-dates-2016-1201776569/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 本剧是以前段日子[[談話節目|脱口秀]]主持人{{Link-en|菲儿·麦格罗|Phil McGraw}}在庭审时的表现为蓝本进行创作。<ref>{{cite web |last=Ausiello |first=Michael |url=http://tvline.com/2016/03/16/michael-weatherly-dr-phil-bull-cbs-drama-series-pilot-cast/ |title=Michael Weatherly Cast as Dr. Phil in ‘Bull’ — CBS Drama Series Pilot |publisher=TVLine |date=2016-03-16 |accessdate=2016-10-08 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308133846/https://tvline.com/2016/03/16/michael-weatherly-dr-phil-bull-cbs-drama-series-pilot-cast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年10月17日，CBS电视网宣布将本剧拓展为23集的完整季播剧。<ref name="Bull, Kevin & MacGyver">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/bull-kevin-can-wait-macgyver-938813?utm_source=twitter|title=‘Bull,’ 'Kevin Can Wait' and ‘MacGyver’ Grab Full-Season Pickups at CBS|last=Stanhope|first=Kate|work=[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]|date=2016-10-17|accessdate=2016-10-17|archive-date=2017-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171031074752/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/bull-kevin-can-wait-macgyver-938813?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2017年3月23日，CBS宣布续订本剧第二季。<ref name="CBS Renewals 2017">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/cbs-early-renewals-macgyver-superior-donuts-life-in-pieces-hawaii-five-0-blue-bloods-1202049276/|title=CBS Renews 5 Freshman & 11 Returning Series, Including 'MacGyver', 'Superior Donuts', 'Life In Pieces' & 'Hawaii Five-O'|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2017-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323163849/http://deadline.com/2017/03/cbs-early-renewals-macgyver-superior-donuts-life-in-pieces-hawaii-five-0-blue-bloods-1202049276/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 剧情提要 ==
《庭审专家》根据一群为庭审统计公司（{{lang|en|Trial Analysis Corporation}}）服务的雇员故事所展开，庭审统计公司是一家由心理学家和“庭审科学”专家杰森·布尔博士所领导的陪审团咨询公司。布尔利用自己和自己团队成员的技能帮助自己的客户挑选合适的陪审员，并协助客户的律师甄选合适的辩护方式来赢取陪审团支持。

